high_descs: Turn to your left and head to the counter top
Pick up the bottle beside the toaster on the counter top
Turn to your left, head to the fridge
Open the fridge, place the bottle on the lower right side of the fridge, close the fridge
Open the fridge, pick up the bottle then turn on your left; head to the cabinet beside the oven
Open the cabinet and put the bottle inside
anns.task_desc: Put the cold bottle in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter and stand in front of the toaster.
Pick the bottle up from next to the toaster.
Go left towards the fridge and turn to face it.
Put the bottle on the bottom shelf and shut the fridge door, then open the door and get the bottle out.
Turn and walk to the cupboard left of the oven.
Open the cabinet and put the bottle in and then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bottle of wine in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the right of the sink
Grab the bottle that is at the back of the counter
Turn left and head to the fridge. Open the bottom door on the fridge.
Put the bottle on the bottom rack of the fridge and close the door. Open the door and take the bottle out. Close the door.
Turn around and walk to the washing machine. Open the door of the cabinet that is to the right of the washing machine.
Place the bottle inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Putting a bottle in a cabinet
